# Open an HTML file that embeds `<style>` (CSS injection) + `<script>`
# (JavaScript injection). All three grammars contribute spans;
# regression in injection routing means fewer total spans.
write index.html <html><head><style>body { color: red; }</style><script>const x = 42;</script></head><body><div class="x">hi</div></body></html>\n
open index.html
expect pane "index.html"
expect screen contains "<style>"
expect screen contains "color: red"
expect highlights at_least 6
